oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Prairie Ramblers - WLS performances - 1941-02-06
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Home recorded Prairie Ramblers performances, as performed on February 6, 1941 on radio station WLS (Chicago, IL). Home recorded flute solo of Andantino also appears on disc.
